messages.content: Summarize the contents of the book Tree of Life by William Blystone

"The Tree of Life: Its Perennial Structure and Symbolism" by William Blystone, published August 31, 2012, serves as a reference and guide to the symbolism of the Tree of Life [goodreads](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGkNMvjRjgqNOhCoSd4w0DwoLUT_q-MO5iT969qGPID9nNejaacxulrej66jluT6bzHB75PDQzSSe2pRETxLNVp2ywdkiRsBYAHGdABQXJoaqAin24F6KfaYvtgn1T9XdJ08VvkrYHjGKccrZwE0a1kVmfJq2cxtA==). Blystone, a Hermetic practitioner, author, and occultist [goodreads](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHg0EstXwy1ED9bOdqutH5CoVt3ukpp3eLOqgWlVo56_YmJ_NaNEOufXAl0QzdIK9YL6S3d23PMhvwZvxq0MfgpitgomFgT2WXNBa0YK4VJbmYUkbJMFIQAJY0va0w4J43TPVOlbbRP6qB4yqC5yFA=) [goodreads](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGkNMvjRjgqNOhCoSd4w0DwoLUT_q-MO5iT969qGPID9nNejaacxulrej66jluT6bzHB75PDQzSSe2pRETxLNVp2ywdkiRsBYAHGdABQXJoaqAin24F6KfaYvtgn1T9XdJ08VvkrYHjGKccrZwE0a1kVmfJq2cxtA==), surveys the origin of the Tree, its original scheme, and traditional doctrine [goodreads](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGkNMvjRjgqNOhCoSd4w0DwoLUT_q-MO5iT969qGPID9nNejaacxulrej66jluT6bzHB75PDQzSSe2pRETxLNVp2ywdkiRsBYAHGdABQXJoaqAin24F6KfaYvtgn1T9XdJ08VvkrYHjGKccrZwE0a1kVmfJq2cxtA==). The book includes illustrations, tables, and plates, and even provides keys to the Greek and Latin alphabets [goodreads](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGkNMvjRjgqNOhCoSd4w0DwoLUT_q-MO5iT969qGPID9nNejaacxulrej66jluT6bzHB75PDQzSSe2pRETxLNVp2ywdkiRsBYAHGdABQXJoaqAin24F6KfaYvtgn1T9XdJ08VvkrYHjGKccrZwE0a1kVmfJq2cxtA==]. Blystone is also the author of "Paenitere: An Introduction to the Occult Arts for the Neophyte" [bookfinder](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGYbcEWzV6X_jAqu_yeDqV6FNxECeQJbWYutaSCpDkIVbzdqeOaKV0iZ6CMJ2JHlGDyYQFGJARlHgcVIzcIstUp1yByONZravRa4_-4A_-QP2gZPQIutgdOhgyEgMU7UfJlMpDo9vFI_lLD1SlD) [goodreads](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFRWYhFSH6iJP4jHqeo-BIFn3TmYSXpXdgNf10Qjud98MDtF9GDfWBegIFZVWC-seXjdFV-ly3qvBbE9Z_WoaTGSjCMpU2IxrXGGaT9VGJ0UKigIqi3MlyUTq-07wqb_jDxvDdSaqS-w7tiT1uZs3Bz7QqbmpbNkog=) [thriftbooks](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH5cgzJx291UFAKaG9ZdAV42MbzwsWM1R9itkSjCzQL2m9nIN-A2qY1AJrhoRymElHPWYtY0DvZp3Z2Wa4mqBE2L6STI6m5gHzg_T1e14DICUhLjlqQy_7ary3srLqf6eI5hPPyAGua3iBdwmj9q_9K8w==).

search_query: William Blystone "Tree of Life" book review summary
Is there a book specifically titled "Tree of Life" written by William Blystone, and if so, what is it about?
web_research_result:
I was unable to find any book review summaries for a book titled "Tree of Life" by William Blystone. However, I did find some potentially relevant information:

*   **Mentions of "Tree of Life":** The "Tree of Life" is mentioned in the context of biology, referring to our evolving understanding of the relationships between living organisms [pearsonhighered](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-0). It is also mentioned in "The Magister 3" by Marcus Katz in relation to the kabbalistic Tree of Life [scribd](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-1). Additionally, "The Tree of Life" is the name of an organization supported by the town of Castine, Maine [castine](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-2).
